重复一遍, 灰狗请呼叫陷阱六号

294
00:24:04,040 --> 00:24:08,955
- ANSWERING MACHINE: Monday, 10:05 a.m.
- Monday? What ever happened to Sunday?
- 星期一, 上午 10:05  - 星期一？星期天哪儿去了？

295
00:24:10,440 --> 00:24:13,637
(SCOFFS) Nonsense. No one sleeps for three days.
胡扯, 没人能一觉睡三天

296
00:24:18,720 --> 00:24:20,711
(PHONE RINGING)

297
00:24:24,600 --> 00:24:26,159
-(STATIC)
- Brendon School.
这里是布伦登学校

298
00:24:27,680 --> 00:24:28,829
Who is this?
是哪位？

299
00:24:28,960 --> 00:24:30,314
SARAH: Hello? Brigadier?
你好, 准将吗？

300
00:24:30,840 --> 00:24:32,990
- This is Sarah-Jane Smith.
- Miss Smith?
- 我是莎拉-简·史密斯  - 史密斯小姐？

301
00:24:33,760 --> 00:24:36,479
Yes. Look, just please listen.
You could be in danger.
是的. 请听我说, 你可能有危险

302
00:24:36,600 --> 00:24:38,432
I've just come from New World University...
我刚从新世界大学出来...

303
00:24:39,280 --> 00:24:40,679
(STATIC) Hello? Brigadier!
能听到吗？准将！

304
00:24:43,640 --> 00:24:45,790
-(PULSATING)
-(PLAYING ON LOOP) Brendon school.
布伦登学校

305
00:24:49,880 --> 00:24:51,075
We have him.
我们找到他了

306
00:24:55,280 --> 00:24:58,318
Hi, kids. Been in any good deprograms lately?
嗨, 孩子们. 最近参加什么好的戒除活动了吗？

307
00:24:58,440 --> 00:24:59,874
Want any autographs?
想要谁的签名不？

308
00:25:00,720 --> 00:25:02,040
If you can read, that is.
要是你会读, 那就是

309
00:25:09,400 --> 00:25:10,435
(DOOR OPENS)

310
00:25:16,760 --> 00:25:20,037
- Looking for something, Anthony?
- A producer with a sense of humour.
- 在找什么吗, 安东尼？  - 找一个有幽默感的制作人

311
00:25:20,160 --> 00:25:22,197
-(CHUCKLES)
- I want a word with the high priestess.
我想和高级女祭司说句话

312
00:25:22,360 --> 00:25:24,158
I'm afraid the vice chancellor's busy.
恐怕副校长这会儿正忙

313
00:25:24,280 --> 00:25:28,114
The conviction I give your propagandist
crap should win me a BAFTA.
我为你们那些坚定信仰搞的宣传, 都可以帮我赢得BAFTA奖了
<i>（BAFTA: 英国电影电视艺术学院奖）</i>

314
00:25:28,240 --> 00:25:30,959
I can't get into my office
for ruddy computer hardware.
我都进不了办公室, 全是那些要命的电脑硬件

315
00:25:31,080 --> 00:25:33,674
Well, it's all part of the new
automated transmitter programme.
哦, 那都是为新的课程自动发送器准备的

316
00:25:33,800 --> 00:25:36,519
Then get the transmitter
to read the scripts. (CHUCKLES)
那你让发送器来念稿子吧

317
00:25:36,640 --> 00:25:38,358
There's no people left here.
这里都没有人了

318
00:25:38,480 --> 00:25:41,598
It's just computers and brain-dead Chillys.
只有电脑和无脑的鸡仔

319
00:25:42,320 --> 00:25:43,833
I'll tell Miss Waterfield.
我会同沃特菲尔德小姐讲的

320
00:25:44,760 --> 00:25:46,831
Tell her I want action now.
告诉她我现在就要看见行动

321
00:25:46,960 --> 00:25:50,590
Not when orders come down from our
Glorious Sponsor, wherever he hangs out.
而不是等我们的荣誉赞助商下命令, 天知道他在哪里闲逛

322
00:25:55,000 --> 00:26:00,234
DISTORTED VOICE: This blind,
empty outer-darkness is unendurable!
这里只有盲目而空虚的黑暗, 令人无法忍受！

323
00:26:01,040 --> 00:26:03,475
Release me now!
现在就释放我吧！

324
00:26:03,600 --> 00:26:06,399
I gave you my word. Soon!
我向你承诺过了, 快了！

325
00:26:11,760 --> 00:26:15,151
(SIGHS) I don't belong in this world.
我不属于这个世界

326
00:26:16,560 --> 00:26:20,076
My family and friends, all lost in time.
我的家庭和朋友, 全都迷失在时间里了

327
00:26:21,720 --> 00:26:24,712
We are both outcast, Victoria.
我俩都是被放逐的人, 维多利亚

328
00:26:25,840 --> 00:26:28,116
That is why we work together.
所以我们要携手

329
00:26:29,600 --> 00:26:31,876
I built you this place,
我给你建了这个地方

330
00:26:32,840 --> 00:26:37,198
with the money my dear father
invested 130 years ago
用了我父亲130年前投资所产生的收益

331
00:26:37,880 --> 00:26:42,238
In return, you promised us
the Light of Truth.
作为回报, 你许诺给我们真相之光

332
00:26:42,360 --> 00:26:45,637
(SCOFFS) There is no Light.
没有什么光

333
00:26:48,480 --> 00:26:50,153
I trust you, Victoria.
我相信你, 维多利亚

334
00:26:51,120 --> 00:26:55,000
One Locus still binds my power.
还有一个人偶困住我的能力

335
00:26:56,120 --> 00:26:58,077
The others were dealt with.
其它的都已经处理掉了

336
00:26:58,600 --> 00:27:02,992
The last must... Will be ready for my return.
最后一个必须...为我的回归做好准备

337
00:27:06,680 --> 00:27:10,116
I think I'm going to scream.
我觉得我要尖叫了

338
00:27:12,520 --> 00:27:14,796
Trap Six, this is Greyhound.
What is your message
陷阱六号, 我是灰狗, 你有什么信息

339
00:27:14,920 --> 00:27:16,354
{STATIC)
{INDISTINCT)

340
00:27:17,880 --> 00:27:20,235
Please repeat, Trap Six.
It's an appalling line.
请再说一遍, 陷阱六号. 这信息很震惊

341
00:27:21,960 --> 00:27:23,030
In London?
在伦敦吗？

342
00:27:24,200 --> 00:27:26,191
Roger, Trap Six, message understood.
收到, 陷阱六号, 明白了

343
00:27:42,280 --> 00:27:44,476
(ENERGY PULSATING)

344
00:27:57,280 --> 00:28:00,272
(CROWD APPLAUDING)

345
00:28:16,760 --> 00:28:18,956
The brigadier's on the move...
准将出动了...

346
00:28:19,160 --> 00:28:20,798
Daniel Hinton?
丹尼尔·辛顿呢？

347
00:28:20,920 --> 00:28:22,194
He fell from the roof.
他从屋顶上掉下去了

348
00:28:23,280 --> 00:28:24,793
What are you saying?
你在说什么？

349
00:28:24,920 --> 00:28:27,309
Just jumped. There's no sign of him below.
他跳下去了, 但下面没有见到他的踪迹

350
00:28:28,400 --> 00:28:29,674
But no one could...
但没人能...

351
00:28:30,880 --> 00:28:32,439
Why didn't you tell me?
你怎么不早告诉我？

352
00:28:33,280 --> 00:28:35,157
Poor Daniel. We must find him!
可怜的丹尼尔. 我们必须找到他！

353
00:28:36,160 --> 00:28:37,480
Let me explain again.
让我再解释一下

354
00:28:38,160 --> 00:28:41,790
He's vanished. His programme's ring-fenced.
他消失了. 他的程序已被“环围住”了

355
00:28:41,920 --> 00:28:43,513
He cannot deprogram himself.
他不可能将他自己反编程掉

356
00:28:44,080 --> 00:28:46,913
Horrible modern terms. You deal with it.
这些现代术语真可怕. 你来处理吧

357
00:28:48,040 --> 00:28:50,509
My task is to prepare the way.
我的任务是铺平道路

358
00:28:51,520 --> 00:28:53,193
Not found the Locus yet then?
还没有找到人偶吗？

359
00:28:54,440 --> 00:28:58,957
Christopher, the chancellor is coming home.
克里斯托弗, 校长要回来了

360
00:29:00,760 --> 00:29:02,831
VICTORIA: It seems the time is now.
看来现在到时候了

361
00:29:03,440 --> 00:29:06,000
I must find the last Locus
我必须找到最后一个人偶

362
00:29:06,680 --> 00:29:10,753
before Daniel's misguided hopes
wreck everything we've worked for.
免得被误导的丹尼尔会破坏我们为之奋斗的一切

363
00:29:24,960 --> 00:29:26,871
Bleeding loaded.
这么多啊

364
00:29:27,800 --> 00:29:30,440
Let it go, will ya? I was only looking!
放手吧, 行吗？我只是看看

365
00:29:53,360 --> 00:29:54,555
(WHISPERS) God.
老天

366
00:29:56,080 --> 00:29:57,036
(SIGHS)

367
00:29:59,200 --> 00:30:00,759
(HORN HONKING)

368
00:30:10,000 --> 00:30:11,115
The Locus...
那个人偶...

369
00:30:26,560 --> 00:30:28,915
I'll break your fingers, you little...
我要掰断你的手指, 你个小...

370
00:30:29,040 --> 00:30:30,917
(FOOTSTEPS)

371
00:30:31,920 --> 00:30:34,036
No, no... (MUFFLED GRUNTING)
不, 不...

372
00:30:34,960 --> 00:30:36,837
(HORNS BLARING)

373
00:30:40,560 --> 00:30:41,880
(BREATHING DEEPLY)

374
00:30:42,920 --> 00:30:46,276
- I'm trying to get through there, but it's worse.
- Yeah. Excuse me...
- 我本打算从这边过去, 但更不好走  - 是, 抱歉...

375
00:30:53,240 --> 00:30:54,435
It's coming closer.
它越来越近了

376
00:30:55,240 --> 00:30:57,629
Perhaps you have something it needs, sir.
也许你手里有它要的东西

377
00:30:58,160 --> 00:31:01,198
After all this time?
I rather doubt that, Hinton.
这么些年以后？我很是怀疑, 辛顿

378
00:31:02,360 --> 00:31:04,317
But you remember what it was, don't you?
但你记得是什么东西, 对吗？

379
00:31:07,920 --> 00:31:09,797
BRIGADIER: I'm not as blinkered as people think.
我并不像人们想象的那么睁眼瞎

380
00:31:10,560 --> 00:31:12,836
It's a sort of mind parasite.
它像是一种意识寄生虫

381
00:31:12,960 --> 00:31:16,237
- The first alien force I ever came up against.
- Sir?
- 是我第一次遭遇的外星力量  - 长官？

382
00:31:16,360 --> 00:31:19,478
In those days it called itself
The Great Intelligence.
那个时候它自称为“大智慧”

383
00:31:19,600 --> 00:31:20,635
And?
还有呢？

384
00:31:20,760 --> 00:31:25,118
No physical shape of its own,
so it enslaved humans as pawns.
它没有它自己的物理形体, 所以它就奴役人类作为它的爪牙

385
00:31:26,000 --> 00:31:30,836
And it deployed a squad of strategic
robots camouflaged like Yeti.
它还部署了一队战斗机器人, 伪装成雪怪的样子

386
00:31:31,520 --> 00:31:32,874
Was this in Tibet, sir?
那是在西藏吗, 长官？

387
00:31:33,720 --> 00:31:36,599
No. London, about 25 years ago.
不, 伦敦, 大概25年前

388
00:31:37,480 --> 00:31:39,949
It invaded the city like a virus,
它像病毒一样入侵了这个城市

389
00:31:40,880 --> 00:31:44,236
using the Underground network
as its nervous system.
把地铁网络用作了它的神经系统

390
00:31:45,440 --> 00:31:48,990
Grisly business. I thought we were
rid of the blighter.
可怕的事情. 我以为我们已经摆脱这个可恶的家伙了

391
00:31:49,120 --> 00:31:50,633
It's still here, sir,
它还在这里, 长官

392
00:31:50,760 --> 00:31:53,434
out on the bardo, the astral plane,
躲在中阴之中, 五行之外
<i>（中阴：藏传佛教术语, 指灵魂处于死后与重生之间时的状态）</i>

393
00:31:53,560 --> 00:31:55,915
trapped outside our physical existence.
被困于我们物理存在之外

394
00:31:56,040 --> 00:31:57,553
BRIGADIER: Is it indeed?
确实吗？

395
00:31:57,680 --> 00:31:58,909
And what does it want?
那它想要什么？

396
00:31:59,040 --> 00:32:00,519
I don't know, sir.
我不知道, 长官

397
00:32:00,640 --> 00:32:01,994
It's you it's hunting.
它在追寻的是你

398
00:32:07,000 --> 00:32:08,035
(GASPS)

399
00:32:12,520 --> 00:32:14,238
What's this got to do with you, Hinton?
但这怎么又跟你扯上了关系, 辛顿？

400
00:32:14,360 --> 00:32:15,839
Just don't trust anyone, sir.
别相信任何人就是了, 长官

401
00:32:15,960 --> 00:32:18,110
- What?  - No one at all.
- 什么？ - 无论是谁

402
00:32:18,880 --> 00:32:22,236
Look, I'll thank you, Hinton,
not to treat me like a complete idiot.
嗯, 我得感谢你, 辛顿, 没把我当做一个完全的傻子

403
00:32:23,440 --> 00:32:25,477
(HORNS BLARING)

404
00:32:31,680 --> 00:32:32,909
(YETI GROWLING)

405
00:32:37,680 --> 00:32:40,433
Damn traffic. Brings out the worst in you,
doesn't it?
可恶的交通, 把每个人最坏的一面都带出来了, 是吧？

406
00:32:41,440 --> 00:32:42,953
(HORN HONKING)

407
00:32:43,720 --> 00:32:44,949
DISTORTED VOICE: Daniel Hinton.
丹尼尔·辛顿

408
00:32:45,760 --> 00:32:47,239
You are summoned.
你被召唤了

409
00:32:47,360 --> 00:32:50,751
(WHIMPERING) Sir, get off me!
先生, 离我远点！

410
00:32:51,960 --> 00:32:53,314
Daniel Hinton!
丹尼尔·辛顿

411
00:32:53,440 --> 00:32:55,477
My summons binds you!
我的召唤困住了你！

412
00:32:58,760 --> 00:33:00,751
MAN: (ON RADIO) Traffic update on New World FM.
新世界FM播报交通状况

413
00:33:00,920 --> 00:33:03,070
ANTHONY: (ON RADIO) I think you'd
better stay home today.
我觉得你们最好今天待在家里

414
00:33:03,200 --> 00:33:05,191
On top of a ton of traffic probs,
除了一大堆交通堵塞

415
00:33:05,320 --> 00:33:08,438
they've just announced that all the
railways and major airports are suspended.
他们刚刚还宣布了所有铁路和主要机场都暂时关闭

416
00:33:08,560 --> 00:33:11,632
<i>So, you'd better get walking 'cause
they're shutting down the tube, too.</i>
所以你最好步行, 因为他们又要关闭隧道了

417
00:33:11,760 --> 00:33:13,876
Crazy. Everything has computer flu.
疯了, 所有东西都患上了电脑病毒似的
<i>(招牌文字: 电脑混沌在蔓延)</i>

418
00:33:14,000 --> 00:33:17,429
So, whatever you do, don't log into your PCs.
所以, 不管你干什么, 都不要登入电脑

419
00:33:17,520 --> 00:33:20,029
They're in a mean mood today.
(ALARM CHIRPS)
它们今天心情很不爽

420
00:33:23,800 --> 00:33:25,757
Can I tell you about the New World, sir?
我能跟你介绍一下新世界吗, 先生？

421
00:33:25,880 --> 00:33:27,154
I'm not interested.
我不感兴趣

422
00:33:27,280 --> 00:33:28,873
We want to tell you about our good news, sir.
我们想跟你说说我们的好消息, 先生

423
00:33:29,000 --> 00:33:30,798
I said I'm not interested.
我说了我不感兴趣

424
00:33:33,440 --> 00:33:34,510
Have a better one.
找个更好的吧

425
00:33:34,640 --> 00:33:38,599
And that's the best of the weather,
brought to you by New World University
这是最好的天气, 新世界大学为你们带来

426
00:33:38,720 --> 00:33:40,358
where the sun always shines.
而阳光永远灿烂

427
00:33:40,880 --> 00:33:41,915
Gridlock out there.
外面交通大堵塞

428
00:33:42,040 --> 00:33:44,190
Is it Friday the 13th, and they didn't tell us?
难道今天是黑色星期五, 而他们没有告诉我们？

429
00:33:44,320 --> 00:33:45,640
Stay at home, give us a call.
待在家里, 给我们打电话

430
00:33:45,760 --> 00:33:48,639
0135-666-416.

431
00:33:48,760 --> 00:33:51,400
And on line one, it's... Danny.
一号线接通了, 这位是...丹尼

432
00:33:51,520 --> 00:33:53,318
Hi, Daniel. What's your problem?
嗨, 丹尼尔, 你什么问题？

433
00:33:53,440 --> 00:33:56,353
HINTON: Anthony, it's me. I'm still alive.
安东尼, 是我, 我还活着

434
00:33:56,480 --> 00:33:58,790
- Listen. It's coming.
- Danny, you idiot. What's happening?
- 听我说, 它要来了  - 丹尼, 你个笨蛋, 都怎么回事？

435
00:33:58,920 --> 00:34:00,274
It's already coming for me,
but it wants all of us.
它已经来找我了, 但它要我们全部

436
00:34:00,400 --> 00:34:02,471
- You've got to warn...
- I knew you'd get caught! Where are you?
- 你必须得警告...  - 我就知道你会被抓住的！你在哪儿？

437
00:34:03,400 --> 00:34:05,437
Danny, you've got to get help before we...
丹尼, 你必须找人帮忙, 否则我们...

438
00:34:06,720 --> 00:34:08,791
Danny! Danny!
丹尼！丹尼！

439
00:34:09,240 --> 00:34:11,629
(ENERGY PULSATING)

440
00:34:16,960 --> 00:34:18,951
{STATIC)
{GROANING)

441
00:34:21,400 --> 00:34:23,835
-(SIGHS)
- What are you after?
你在追寻什么？

442
00:34:25,440 --> 00:34:26,839
Bloody Chillys.
要命的鸡仔

443
00:34:27,640 --> 00:34:30,154
- I'm going to get the law.
- Think they'd believe you?
- 我打算去找执法部门了  - 觉得他们会相信你？

444
00:34:31,320 --> 00:34:33,914
Sir, I never hurt no one.
先生, 我从没伤害过任何人

445
00:34:34,040 --> 00:34:37,032
Not me, sir. Not old Harrods.
我没有, 先生, 老哈罗斯没有

446
00:34:38,480 --> 00:34:39,515
(SHOUTS) Don't!
不要！

447
00:34:41,160 --> 00:34:42,275
Sir,
先生

448
00:34:44,000 --> 00:34:45,991
flew right down, you did.
飞下来了, 你那时候

449
00:34:46,120 --> 00:34:49,511
Glided down out of that place. (LAUGHS)
从那个地方滑下来了

450
00:34:50,240 --> 00:34:52,675
Don't need jets no more, sir?
不再需要滑翔机了吗, 先生？

451
00:34:52,800 --> 00:34:56,589
And then he comes after us,
like an old spidery man.
然后他就开始追着我们, 像一只老蜘蛛

452
00:34:57,040 --> 00:34:58,519
He's coming after all of us.
他在追我们所有人

453
00:35:00,120 --> 00:35:03,317
Listen, that money you nicked from me
is no good to anyone. Period!
听着, 你从我身上摸走的钱对谁也用了. 句号！

454
00:35:03,440 --> 00:35:04,874
Not unless you help me!
除非你帮助我！

455
00:35:06,120 --> 00:35:07,235
You got more?
你还有吗？

456
00:35:09,600 --> 00:35:12,319
Sir, 1 got principles.
先生, 我有原则的

457
00:35:12,960 --> 00:35:14,519
I'm very particular.
我非常挑剔

458
00:35:16,360 --> 00:35:17,680
You've seen what's coming,
你看到什么东西会来

459
00:35:20,240 --> 00:35:22,277
but it's only half what I see.
但不及我所看到的一半

460
00:35:22,720 --> 00:35:25,234
Come on, there's someone we have to reach fast.
快, 我们必须得尽快找到一个人

461
00:35:34,960 --> 00:35:37,634
- Good morning.
- Hi. How can I help you?
- 早上好  - 嗨, 有什么可以帮你的吗？

462
00:35:37,760 --> 00:35:39,080
Lethbridge-Stewart for Cavendish.
利斯布里奇-斯图尔特, 来找凯文迪许

463
00:35:39,200 --> 00:35:41,111
Right. If you'd like to go through
to the lounge, Brigadier,
好, 如果你走过休息室, 准将

464
00:35:41,240 --> 00:35:44,153
you'll find Captain Cavendish
already waiting for you.
你就会发现凯文迪许队长已经在等你

465
00:35:45,040 --> 00:35:49,273
"John Jerum, soldierman,
Is searching high and low.
"John Jerum, 兵哥哥, 上下求索着"

466
00:35:50,280 --> 00:35:54,877
"The only secret he can keep
Is one he doesn't know.”
“唯一能保住的秘密, 是他自己也不知道的”

467
00:35:57,040 --> 00:35:58,872
My father used to say that.
我父亲经常念这句

468
00:35:59,960 --> 00:36:01,439
He'd have hated this.
他肯定恨这个

469
00:36:03,360 --> 00:36:05,510
You haven't got a clue, have you?
你一点都不知道, 是吧

470
00:36:06,320 --> 00:36:09,438
Your precious Chancellor's
got all the real power,
你那宝贵的校长拥有所有真正的能力

471
00:36:09,560 --> 00:36:11,551
the power we can all profit by.
我们都可以从这些能力里受益

472
00:36:12,840 --> 00:36:15,639
He isn't just some
father substitute for you.
他可不是你那什么父亲的小替身

473
00:36:15,760 --> 00:36:18,754
He works for the world's spiritual good,
他致力于建立一个很好的精神世界

474
00:36:19,000 --> 00:36:21,032
but you'd even sell your own soul.
但你却把自己的灵魂都卖了

475
00:36:21,160 --> 00:36:23,720
(CHUCKLES) That's marketing.
这是市场营销

476
00:36:24,680 --> 00:36:26,717
All "ring-fenced” no doubt.
都被“环围住”了, 毫无疑问

477
00:36:28,120 --> 00:36:29,952
Like your expense account.
就像你的支出账户

478
00:36:31,320 --> 00:36:32,833
ANTHONY: (LOUDSPEAKERS)
Victoria Waterfield!
维多利亚•沃特菲尔德!

479
00:36:33,480 --> 00:36:34,754
Can you hear me?
你能听到我吗？

480
00:36:35,400 --> 00:36:38,870
Miss Waterfield's our boss,
ladies and gentlemen,
沃特菲尔德小姐是我们的老板, 女士们先生们

481
00:36:39,000 --> 00:36:41,958
- the big cheese at N Treble U!
- Make him stop! Stop him!
- 她是 NTU 的大人物！  - 让他停下来！阻止他！

482
00:36:42,080 --> 00:36:44,276
-(CHUCKLES)
- And she's today's surprise guest
她是今天的神秘嘉宾

483
00:36:44,400 --> 00:36:46,073
on “Lift the Lid.”
来到“揭开盖子”栏目

484
00:36:46,200 --> 00:36:48,794
So, ring in those questions now.
好, 现在打电话进来提问吧

485
00:36:48,920 --> 00:36:52,072
It's revelation time, Vice Chancellor!
到了揭晓的时间了, 副校长！

486
00:36:53,120 --> 00:36:56,112
Forget anything I said before. It was lies!
忘了我以前说过的话吧, 都是谎言！

487
00:36:56,640 --> 00:36:58,870
New World's just a big front.
新世界只是一个大幌子

488
00:36:59,000 --> 00:37:01,958
But they pay well, don't they,
Miss Waterfield?
不过他们薪水不错, 是吧, 沃特菲尔德小姐？

489
00:37:02,800 --> 00:37:05,110
(ENERGY PULSATING) What about
all the people that disappear, eh?
但那些失踪的人呢, 嗯？

490
00:37:05,240 --> 00:37:06,639
Danny was right!
丹尼说对了！

491
00:37:06,760 --> 00:37:09,229
New World doesn't give a toss for you.
新世界并不在乎你

492
00:37:09,360 --> 00:37:10,430
Something's coming.
有东西来了

493
00:37:10,920 --> 00:37:12,831
Victoria Waterfield will tell you.
维多利亚•沃特菲尔德会告诉你们的

494
00:37:14,000 --> 00:37:15,399
(SOBBING) She'll tell you.
她会告诉你们

495
00:37:16,120 --> 00:37:19,476
And it'll finish everything.
那东西会结束这一切

496
00:37:32,000 --> 00:37:34,560
- Good to see you, Brigadier.
- Sorry I'm late, Cavendish.
- 很高兴见到你, 准将  - 抱歉我来晚了, 凯文迪许

497
00:37:34,680 --> 00:37:37,638
The transport system seems to be
fouled up by this computer business.
交通系统似乎被电脑问题搞瘫痪了

498
00:37:37,760 --> 00:37:40,434
- Mmm, quite. Would you care for a drink?
- No, thank you.
- 唔, 太差了. 你介意喝一杯吗？  - 不, 谢谢你

499
00:37:41,080 --> 00:37:42,798
I thought it best to meet here.
我觉得在这里见面最好

500
00:37:42,920 --> 00:37:45,639
Security boys get a bit stressed out
over ID checks.
负责安全的小伙子们总是要紧张兮兮地查证件

501
00:37:46,280 --> 00:37:48,920
So, UNIT hasn't changed since my time, eh?
看来, 我走之后 UNIT 还没变, 嗯？

502
00:37:49,040 --> 00:37:51,554
Well, I doubt there'd be much left
that you'd recognise.
哦, 我怀疑还有多少你能认出来

503
00:37:51,680 --> 00:37:54,149
Razor-smart weapons,
all are computers these days.
Razor-smart 的武器, 现在全是电脑了

504
00:37:55,080 --> 00:37:58,357
I used to leave the technology to the experts.
我那时都把技术问题留给专家们

505
00:37:58,480 --> 00:38:00,118
Yes, of course.
是, 当然

506
00:38:01,360 --> 00:38:04,193
Do you know they called your era
"The Blunder Days"?
你知道他们把你们那个时代叫做“Blunder时代”吗？

507
00:38:04,320 --> 00:38:06,516
- The what?
- Blood and Thunder.
- 什么时代？  - 热血和雷霆

508
00:38:06,640 --> 00:38:08,756
Well, you took on
some formidable opposition.
看, 你碰上过一些强硬的对手

509
00:38:08,880 --> 00:38:11,713
Cybermen, demons, Yeti.
赛博人, 恶魔, 雪怪

510
00:38:12,760 --> 00:38:16,833
No worse than jumped up officers
with tuppenny-halfpenny commissions.
那也不如某些军官厉害, 他们靠着一两个便士的任务就升了上来

511
00:38:17,720 --> 00:38:19,074
Right.
对

512
00:38:19,200 --> 00:38:22,192
Cavendish, exactly why did you call me
up to town today?
凯文迪许, 你今天到底是为了什么把我叫进城来？

513
00:38:22,320 --> 00:38:24,072
Information, sir,
资料, 长官

514
00:38:25,480 --> 00:38:28,074
of a personal nature, you understand?
关于一点个人性质的, 明白吗？

515
00:38:28,200 --> 00:38:29,474
Meaning?
意思是...？

516
00:38:29,600 --> 00:38:31,989
Someone's been hacking
into security files in Geneva.
有人黑进了日内瓦的保密文件

517
00:38:32,120 --> 00:38:33,713
My files, I take it.
我的文件, 我懂了

518
00:38:33,840 --> 00:38:36,832
Yes, so the MOD were never very
forthcoming about dealings with UNIT.
是的, 在处理UNIT相关事情时国防部总是不太积极

519
00:38:36,960 --> 00:38:39,873
Besides, we need more personal details.
而且, 我们需要多一些个人信息

520
00:38:40,000 --> 00:38:40,956
We?
我们？

521
00:38:41,680 --> 00:38:44,433
Do I take it that security is
in the dark about this, too?
我能否理解为安全部门对此还不知情？

522
00:38:45,640 --> 00:38:48,473
Strange you never rose
above Brigadier, wasn't it?
奇怪的是你做准将之后再也没有升职过, 是吗？

523
00:38:49,160 --> 00:38:50,798
Internal politics.
内部政治嘛

524
00:38:52,080 --> 00:38:55,357
Well, I had no idea there was a market
for my memoirs.
啊, 我还不知道我的回忆录还挺有市场

525
00:38:56,200 --> 00:38:58,589
I'll send you a copy
when I get round to writing them.
等我有时间写完的话, 我会送你一本

526
00:39:05,040 --> 00:39:09,600
So, UNIT got all the blame
for blowing up the church.
所以, 炸掉教堂的事情就全是 UNIT 背锅了？
<i>（这应该是指第八季第五集《恶魔》The Dæmons中发生的事情）</i>

527
00:39:10,040 --> 00:39:12,554
- Are you sure you won't join me, Brigadier?
- Quite sure.
- 你确定不陪我来一杯, 准将？ - 相当确定

528
00:39:14,360 --> 00:39:17,079
You must've picked up
the odd souvenir in your time.
你那时肯定拿过一些奇怪的东西

529
00:39:17,960 --> 00:39:21,396
I counted them in
and I counted them all back out.
收进来的时候我数过, 放回去的时候我也全都数过

530
00:39:21,520 --> 00:39:24,114
No particular keepsake?
没有什么特别的纪念品？

531
00:39:24,240 --> 00:39:25,913
I mean, things do get mislaid.
我是说, 弄丢什么东西

532
00:39:26,400 --> 00:39:29,597
If you lose things,
you could lose men, too.
如果你弄丢东西, 你也会弄丢人

533
00:39:30,360 --> 00:39:33,876
Well, it's been good to talk to you, Cavendish.
but I have another appointment.
好了, 很高兴同你聊聊. 凯文迪许. 但我还有另外一个约

534
00:39:34,000 --> 00:39:36,640
So soon? I was concerned, Brigadier.
这么快？我很担心, 准将？

535
00:39:36,760 --> 00:39:38,876
- So was I
- CAVENDISH: So you should be.
- 我也是  - 你也该这样

536
00:39:40,440 --> 00:39:41,919
Blood and Thunder, Captain.
热血与雷霆, 队长

537
00:39:42,040 --> 00:39:43,394
Now back off.
现在退后

538
00:39:44,040 --> 00:39:45,360
I'm leaving.
我走了

539
00:39:48,200 --> 00:39:49,759
Get after him!
去追他！

540
00:39:52,360 --> 00:39:53,794
It's not too late!
还不算太迟！

541
00:39:54,560 --> 00:39:56,198
I must find it.
我必须找到它

542
00:39:56,960 --> 00:39:59,634
(PYRAMID PULSATING)

543
00:39:59,760 --> 00:40:03,276
DISTORTED VOICE: Victoria, I am here.
维多利亚, 我在这里

544
00:40:21,520 --> 00:40:23,511
(DISTORTED) Where is the Locus?
人偶在哪里？

545
00:40:24,880 --> 00:40:26,871
(HORNS BLARING)

546
00:40:32,360 --> 00:40:37,996
All right then.
Quote them the codes, NN and then QQ.
那好吧, 告诉他们代号, NN 和 QQ
<i>(分别指《可恶的雪人》和《恐惧之网》对应事件,
其实它们是相应电视剧集的生产代号)</i>

547
00:40:38,760 --> 00:40:42,037
It's a risk, but we must reach
someone we can trust.
这是个风险, 但我们必须找到一个我们可以信任的人

548
00:40:57,400 --> 00:40:59,471
(STATIC)

549
00:41:00,840 --> 00:41:05,437
- MAN: (ON PHONE) Q?
- No, I said codes NN and Q... QQ!
- Q?  - 不, 我说了, 代号是 NN 和 Q .. QQ！

550
00:41:05,560 --> 00:41:06,959
- It's urgent!
- I see, thank you.
- 这事很紧急！  - 明白了, 谢谢你

551
00:41:07,080 --> 00:41:08,400
I'd get more sense from a tea lady.
找个女服务员都比你明白

552
00:41:08,520 --> 00:41:10,272
May I ask if you've encountered
anything resembling a Yeti?
我可以问问, 你是遇到了某种像是雪怪的东西？

553
00:41:10,400 --> 00:41:12,630
- Have I encountered any what?
- A Yeti.
- 我是遇到了什么？ - 雪怪！

554
00:41:12,760 --> 00:41:14,671
What have Yeti got to do with it?
雪怪跟这有什么关系？

555
00:41:21,640 --> 00:41:23,677
- You're late.
- I was delayed.
- 你迟到了  - 我被拖住了

556
00:41:23,800 --> 00:41:26,679
The traffic and this computer business...
堵车和电脑方面的问题...

557
00:41:26,800 --> 00:41:29,360
- Are you all right?
- Oh, I can't complain.
- 你还好吗？  - 噢, 没什么可抱怨的

558
00:41:29,480 --> 00:41:30,709
How are you?
你好吗？

559
00:41:31,520 --> 00:41:32,954
Look, this is stupid.
看, 这事很愚蠢

560
00:41:33,080 --> 00:41:34,514
I'll just go. I shouldn't have called you.
我还是走吧, 不应该给你打电话的

561
00:41:34,640 --> 00:41:37,758
Look, Kate, have you eaten?
We could get a meal.
嗯, 凯特, 你吃了吗？我们可以去吃个饭

562
00:41:37,880 --> 00:41:39,757
No. Ugh...
不, 呃...

563
00:41:39,880 --> 00:41:42,679
- All right, er, we'll sit here.
- 1... (SIGHS)
- 没事, 嗯, 我们就这里坐坐  - 我...

564
00:41:43,880 --> 00:41:45,518
I'm sorry, Dad.
对不起, 爸爸

565
00:41:49,440 --> 00:41:50,794
You look tired.
你看起来很累

566
00:41:50,920 --> 00:41:52,399
I've had a difficult morning.
我这一早上过得很糟糕

567
00:41:53,880 --> 00:41:56,190
Kate, it's been six years.
凯特, 这都六年了

568
00:41:56,320 --> 00:41:57,515
What's the matter? Is it money?
出什么事呢？是因为钱吗？

569
00:41:57,640 --> 00:41:58,994
No, no. Not especially.
不, 不. 并不是

570
00:41:59,120 --> 00:42:01,794
- Your mother then?
- No! I don't see her either.
- 那是你母亲？  - 不！我也没见她

571
00:42:02,840 --> 00:42:05,400
Look, I know this is crazy, but...
看, 我知道这很疯狂, 但是...

572
00:42:05,520 --> 00:42:07,113
- I'm being harassed.
- Who by?
- 我被骚扰了  - 被谁？

573
00:42:07,800 --> 00:42:09,677
- There are these Chillys.
- Chillys?
- 就那些鸡仔  - 鸡仔?

574
00:42:09,800 --> 00:42:11,393
- You know? Children...
-(EXCLAIMS) Children?
- 你知道吗, 一些孩子...  - 孩子？

575
00:42:11,520 --> 00:42:14,433
I mean they're called Children
from this New World techno-cult.
我是说他们被一个新世界的科技崇拜团队称为孩子

576
00:42:14,560 --> 00:42:15,709
Two of them.
有两个人

577
00:42:15,840 --> 00:42:17,751
They just sit opposite the boat
all the time.
他们一直坐在船的对面

578
00:42:17,880 --> 00:42:19,917
- Look, I'm being stupid.
- No.
- 看, 我是个蠢人...  - 不

579
00:42:20,040 --> 00:42:21,951
But they just won't go away.
但他们就是不走

580
00:42:22,080 --> 00:42:25,118
And they're frightening...
And they're frightening me.
而且他们很吓人...他们让我害怕了

581
00:42:26,240 --> 00:42:27,560
Chancellor.
校长

582
00:42:33,520 --> 00:42:36,751
Welcome home, Professor Travers.
欢迎回来, 特拉弗斯教授

583
00:42:36,880 --> 00:42:39,838
(DISTORTED) I am still in the wilderness.
我还在荒野里

584
00:42:41,520 --> 00:42:45,639
Only my will to survive
keeps me from despair.
都是我求生的欲望才使我免于绝望

585
00:42:46,520 --> 00:42:49,399
You have lit a flame of hope in all of us.
你在我们中间点起了希望的火焰

586
00:42:51,520 --> 00:42:54,956
It is as I instructed.
它是按照我的指示

587
00:42:56,080 --> 00:42:58,435
Symmetry. Shape.
对称. 形状

588
00:42:58,560 --> 00:43:02,349
My form at last,
最后是我的形体

589
00:43:02,480 --> 00:43:04,630
shaping out my future!
决定了我的未来！

590
00:43:07,280 --> 00:43:12,150
When will my new web
stretch out across the Earth?
什么时候我的新网才能延伸到整个地球？

591
00:43:12,280 --> 00:43:13,236
Web?
网？

592
00:43:14,280 --> 00:43:19,354
Only when I have found the final Locus!
只有等我找到最后的人偶！

593
00:43:20,400 --> 00:43:21,959
But what about, erm...
但那个谁, 嗯...

594
00:43:22,080 --> 00:43:23,673
What's his name? Doesn't he help?
他的名字是什么来着？他帮不上忙吗？

595
00:43:23,800 --> 00:43:25,791
I split up with Jonathan two years ago.
我同乔纳森分开了, 两年前

596
00:43:25,920 --> 00:43:27,319
I'm sorry.
对不起

597
00:43:27,440 --> 00:43:29,033
I'm getting old.
我老了

598
00:43:29,160 --> 00:43:30,673
Perhaps you should get off that boat.
也许你应该离开那艘船

599
00:43:30,800 --> 00:43:32,598
It's not the boat. It's them!
问题不是船, 是他们！

600
00:43:33,240 --> 00:43:34,992
- And me too?
- Well,
- 我也是吗？  - 怎么说呢

601
00:43:35,800 --> 00:43:38,394
army families get to live together,
so why didn't we?
军人家庭一般都住在一起, 为什么我们不是？

602
00:43:38,520 --> 00:43:40,318
Was your career that important?
你的事业就那么重要？

603
00:43:41,880 --> 00:43:44,235
I'm afraid I can't explain, Kate.
恐怕我没法解释, 凯特

604
00:43:44,360 --> 00:43:46,874
Mum used to think that
you were some sort of spy.
妈妈曾经以为, 你是某种间谍

605
00:43:47,000 --> 00:43:49,514
We used to hope it, because at least
that would be interesting.
我们曾经都盼望过, 因为那样的话就会很有意思

606
00:43:50,280 --> 00:43:51,679
But it's just soldiers, isn't it?
但你只是一个士兵, 是吗？

607
00:43:52,320 --> 00:43:55,073
Training to kill people with big guns.
被训练成用大枪去杀人

608
00:43:55,200 --> 00:43:56,918
I had other responsibilities.
我扛着其它一些责任

609
00:43:57,040 --> 00:43:58,519
Well, who to?
哦, 对谁的责任？

610
00:43:58,640 --> 00:44:00,597
To everyone.
对每一个人

611
00:44:00,720 --> 00:44:02,154
What?
什么？

612
00:44:02,280 --> 00:44:03,236
That's all.
只能说这么多

613
00:44:03,360 --> 00:44:05,636
(OMINOUS MUSIC PLAYING)

614
00:44:09,320 --> 00:44:10,799
Who do I trust, then?
那, 我信任谁？

615
00:44:12,320 --> 00:44:16,234
Don't trust anyone, sir.
I told you, no one at all.
别相信任何人, 长官. 我告诉过你, 无论是谁

616
00:44:20,200 --> 00:44:22,032
Are you sure you don't want any money?
你确定不想要些钱吗？

617
00:44:22,160 --> 00:44:23,639
Oh, just forget it then.
噢, 忘了这事算了

618
00:44:24,760 --> 00:44:26,273
Kate. Kate, wait!
凯特, 凯特, 等等！

619
00:44:27,520 --> 00:44:29,796
(HOUSE MUSIC PLAYING THROUGH HEADPHONES)

620
00:44:33,160 --> 00:44:36,312
Hello again, Granddad. We want you.
又遇到了, 老爷爷, 我们在找你

621
00:44:36,440 --> 00:44:37,396
Argh!
啊！

622
00:44:48,720 --> 00:44:49,869
Good Lord...
好家伙...

623
00:44:50,400 --> 00:44:52,357
Is that you?
是你吗？

624
00:44:52,480 --> 00:44:55,552
Have you changed yourself again?
你又变样子了？
<i>（显然这里准将以为这又是博士的新化身）</i>

625
00:44:59,920 --> 00:45:05,157
<i>Om mani padme hum</i>
<i>(唵嘛呢叭咪吽)</i>

626
00:45:05,120 --> 00:45:07,157
I needed time!
我需要时间!

627
00:45:07,840 --> 00:45:09,513
DISTORTED VOICE: I needed freedom!
我需要自由！

628
00:45:10,240 --> 00:45:12,072
You're not Professor Travers!
你不是特拉弗斯教授！

629
00:45:12,200 --> 00:45:13,679
-(LAUGHING)
- A pity shame!
可怜可耻！

630
00:45:13,800 --> 00:45:15,598
Let me go!
放开我！

631
00:45:15,720 --> 00:45:17,870
Your task is done.
你的任务完成了

632
00:45:18,000 --> 00:45:20,435
Now, I take control!
现在, 我来掌握控制权！

633
00:45:21,480 --> 00:45:23,073
Let me go!
放开我

634
00:45:23,720 --> 00:45:25,279
Who are you?
你是谁？

635
00:45:25,920 --> 00:45:27,831
Remember me, Victoria?
记得我吗, 维多利亚？

636
00:45:28,480 --> 00:45:30,551
Who's blind now?
现在谁是瞎子？

637
00:45:34,280 --> 00:45:36,032
- Hello, Dad.  - Kate.
- 嗨, 爸爸  - 凯特

638
00:45:37,240 --> 00:45:38,753
- Where am I?  - On the boat.
- 我在哪儿？  - 在船上

639
00:45:38,880 --> 00:45:39,870
We had to bring you here.
我们只能带你来这里

640
00:45:40,000 --> 00:45:42,674
Daniel Hinton, Brigadier. School House 91.
我是丹尼尔·辛顿, 准将. 布伦登学校91届

641
00:45:43,400 --> 00:45:45,437
I remember. Thank you.
我记得. 谢谢你

642
00:45:46,600 --> 00:45:48,159
But we met quite recently. Am I right?
但我们最近碰过面, 我说得对吗？

643
00:45:48,280 --> 00:45:50,715
On something called the astral plane?
在一个被称为意识层面的地方？

644
00:45:50,840 --> 00:45:52,319
It wasn't entirely wasted then.
看来没有全白费

645
00:45:52,440 --> 00:45:53,760
Extraordinary.
令人惊奇

646
00:45:55,040 --> 00:45:56,838
Hello? We're moving.
怎么？我们在走

647
00:46:01,560 --> 00:46:03,073
Dad, I thought it would be best if...
爸爸, 我觉得最好还是...

648
00:46:03,200 --> 00:46:04,634
Sir... Glad to see you're all right, sir.
长官...很高兴看见你没事, 长官

649
00:46:04,760 --> 00:46:06,671
Harrods saved you from the Chillys.
哈罗斯从鸡仔手中救了你

650
00:46:06,800 --> 00:46:08,279
Bunch of hooligans, sir.
一群小流氓而已, 长官

651
00:46:08,400 --> 00:46:09,754
Best off well away from them.
最好离他们远一点

652
00:46:09,880 --> 00:46:12,235
Well, thank you, erm... Harrods?
好, 谢谢你, 呃...哈罗斯？

653
00:46:12,360 --> 00:46:13,350
Sir.
是

654
00:46:13,480 --> 00:46:15,756
Army, aren't you? On your uppers?
军人, 对不？看你鞋帮(?)

655
00:46:15,880 --> 00:46:21,193
RAF, sir. Flight Sergeant Haroldson.
Squadron got disbanded, sir.
皇家空军, 长官. 空军上士哈罗德森. 中队编制被取消了, 长官

656
00:46:22,320 --> 00:46:24,072
Like losing your family.
就像没了家一样

657
00:46:26,160 --> 00:46:29,596
Get called Harrods
'cause I'm fussy where I kip down.
被叫做哈罗斯, 因为我对于睡觉的地方很挑剔

658
00:46:29,720 --> 00:46:32,155
- Alright, Flight Sergeant. Carry on.
- Sir.
- 好吧, 空军上士, 继续  - 是

659
00:46:34,720 --> 00:46:37,678
I must say, Kate,
the company you keep's an eye-opener.
我必须要说, 凯特, 你这些朋友很让人开眼

660
00:46:37,800 --> 00:46:39,199
Oh, I thought they were with you.
哦, 我还以为他们是你一伙儿的

661
00:46:39,320 --> 00:46:42,278
We can't stay here, Brigadier,
the Intelligence is hunting us.
我们不能待在这里, 准将. 大智慧在搜寻我们

662
00:46:42,400 --> 00:46:46,030
The both of us? Are you one of these
Chilly characters too?
我们两个都是？你不也是那些鸡仔中的一员吗？

663
00:46:46,560 --> 00:46:49,518
New World's a front to bring
the Intelligence back through,
新世界只是一个外壳, 意图是要把大智慧带回来

664
00:46:49,640 --> 00:46:51,472
an evil spirit that
got bound to the Earth.
那是个恶灵, 被困到地球了

665
00:46:52,080 --> 00:46:56,074
Listen to you two. I mean, who do I
call first, police or psychiatrist?
听听你们两个. 我是说, 我应该先打电话给谁, 警察还是精神病医生？

666
00:46:56,200 --> 00:46:59,079
Trust no one. Isn't that right, Hinton?
别信任何人. 这没错吧, 辛顿？

667
00:46:59,200 --> 00:47:02,397
- Not even my people at the UNIT.
- The whole city's fouled up.
- 即使是我那些 UNIT 的人  - 整个城市都混乱了

668
00:47:02,520 --> 00:47:04,909
The computer Internet's virally infested.
电脑互联网已经被病毒入侵了

669
00:47:05,040 --> 00:47:07,077
And that's the Intelligence's new body?
那就是大智慧的新形体？

670
00:47:08,080 --> 00:47:09,275
It won't stop there.
它不会止步于此的

671
00:47:14,560 --> 00:47:16,358
(BEEPING)

672
00:47:16,480 --> 00:47:19,598
The Intelligence was driven out.
I was there.
大智慧被赶走了, 当时我在那里

673
00:47:19,720 --> 00:47:23,315
No. It's trapped until all its old
icons of power can be destroyed.
没有, 它只是被困住了, 除非把它所有的权力图腾都摧毁

674
00:47:24,120 --> 00:47:27,317
One link still remains, the final Locus.
有一个链接还在, 最后那个人偶

675
00:47:27,440 --> 00:47:29,317
- Well, how do you know?
- Just do.
- 哦, 你怎么知道？  - 就是知道

676
00:47:30,520 --> 00:47:33,239
Cavendish asked me about keepsakes.
卡文迪许问过我是否保留了纪念品

677
00:47:33,360 --> 00:47:34,509
And now that I think of it,
现在我再想想

678
00:47:34,640 --> 00:47:36,278
- there was something.
- Yes?
- 好像是有某个东西  - 是吗？

679
00:47:36,400 --> 00:47:37,913
But I lost that years ago.
但多年以前弄丢了

680
00:47:38,040 --> 00:47:38,996
Like what?
什么样子的？

681
00:47:39,640 --> 00:47:42,837
A small carving of a Yeti,
like a chess piece.
一个雪怪一样的小雕像, 像一个象棋棋子

682
00:47:42,960 --> 00:47:44,234
Tibetan, I think.
西藏的东西, 我想是

683
00:47:45,240 --> 00:47:46,196
Dad...
爸爸...

684
00:47:48,160 --> 00:47:49,753
(BEEPING)

685
00:48:05,120 --> 00:48:06,235
Like this?
就像这个？

686
00:48:07,280 --> 00:48:09,669
Yes. That's it.
是的, 就是它

687
00:48:09,800 --> 00:48:11,393
I've had it since I was little.
我很小的时候拿了它

688
00:48:11,520 --> 00:48:14,194
It's infinitely dangerous.
We must get rid of it now.
这东西非常的危险, 我们必须马上甩掉它

689
00:48:14,880 --> 00:48:15,950
(CRASHING)

690
00:48:16,080 --> 00:48:17,275
Sir?
长官？

691
00:48:17,600 --> 00:48:18,920
Sir, we have company.
长官, 有客人来了

692
00:48:22,720 --> 00:48:24,870
No, get them away! Get them away!
不, 把他们弄走！把他们弄走！

693
00:48:25,000 --> 00:48:26,911
- Everyone, out, now!
- I'm sorry, Brigadier.
- 所有人, 出去, 马上！  - 抱歉, 准将

694
00:48:27,040 --> 00:48:28,394
Out of the way, Hinton.
别碍事, 辛顿

695
00:48:28,520 --> 00:48:29,999
I didn't know, I swear it.
我不知道, 我发誓

696
00:48:30,120 --> 00:48:31,519
What are you on about?
你这是干什么？

697
00:48:31,640 --> 00:48:34,359
I warned you! Don't trust anyone!
我告诉过你！不要相信任何人！

698
00:48:34,480 --> 00:48:37,438
The Intelligence used me to seek you out.
I'm the trap!
大智慧利用我来把你挖出来, 我就是诱饵！

699
00:48:37,560 --> 00:48:39,631
I'm warning you, Hinton, stand back!
我警告你, 辛顿, 后退！

700
00:48:39,760 --> 00:48:41,273
- Give me the Locus.
- KATE: No.
- 把人偶给我  - 不

701
00:48:41,680 --> 00:48:43,398
No guns. Not here!
不要开枪, 这里不行！

702
00:48:43,520 --> 00:48:46,114
- Get back!
-(BEEPING)
后退!

703
00:48:52,920 --> 00:48:54,991
(ROARING)

704
00:49:02,920 --> 00:49:04,035
(GROWLING)

705
00:49:17,640 --> 00:49:19,597
What's happening? This is my home.
发生了什么？这里是我家

706
00:49:20,320 --> 00:49:23,233
Well, they got what they want
and now they're going.
喏, 他们得到了他们想要的东西, 现在就撤了

707
00:49:23,960 --> 00:49:25,837
Back to the New World, sir.
回新世界去了, 长官

708
00:49:25,960 --> 00:49:27,553
That's where it all comes from.
他们都来自那个地方

709
00:49:27,680 --> 00:49:29,273
What sort of job do you do?
你干的是什么工作？

710
00:49:29,400 --> 00:49:31,357
- That boy...
- I have to get after them, Kate.
- 那个孩子...  - 我必须得去追他们, 凯特

711
00:49:31,480 --> 00:49:32,800
I'll explain later.
我后面再解释

712
00:49:32,920 --> 00:49:34,194
Just go, then.
走吧, 那就

713
00:49:34,320 --> 00:49:35,390
Flight Sergeant?
空军上士？

714
00:49:35,520 --> 00:49:37,875
I'll come, sir. For the lad's sake.
我也去, 长官. 为了那个小伙子

715
00:49:38,000 --> 00:49:39,229
Good man.
好人

716
00:49:39,360 --> 00:49:40,998
Er, wait outside, will you?
呃, 外面等一下, 好吗？

717
00:49:41,120 --> 00:49:42,076
Sir.
是

718
00:49:45,600 --> 00:49:47,034
- Kate.  - What?
- 凯特  - 什么？

719
00:49:47,760 --> 00:49:48,955
Just tell me one thing.
就告诉我一件事情

720
00:49:50,080 --> 00:49:52,356
Why do you keep a box of toys down there?
为什么你在这里存了一箱玩具？

721
00:49:59,760 --> 00:50:01,273
He'll be five, next week.
他就要满五岁了, 下个星期

722
00:50:04,720 --> 00:50:06,631
(SOFTLY) I have a grandson!
我有一个外孙了！

723
00:50:08,240 --> 00:50:11,119
My grandson!
我的外孙！

724
00:50:11,240 --> 00:50:13,038
I never dreamt...
我从没梦想过...

725
00:50:14,120 --> 00:50:15,076
Good Lord.
好家伙

726
00:50:15,800 --> 00:50:16,756
Gordon.
他叫戈登

727
00:50:17,640 --> 00:50:19,313
Gordon James, after you.
戈登-詹姆斯, 用你的名取得

728
00:50:20,800 --> 00:50:22,598
He's safe, away from here.
他很安全, 不在这里

729
00:50:23,520 --> 00:50:24,555
Oh, I'm sorry.
哦, 对不起

730
00:50:24,680 --> 00:50:26,751
(SNIFFLES) My grandson.
我的外孙

731
00:50:27,640 --> 00:50:29,313
Kate, can I keep this?
凯特, 我能留着这个吗？

732
00:50:29,760 --> 00:50:31,398
It's getting late.
时候不早了

733
00:50:31,520 --> 00:50:33,557
We'll talk later. I'll be back.
我们晚些再谈, 我会回来的

734
00:50:43,640 --> 00:50:45,677
(GROWLING)

735
00:50:50,480 --> 00:50:51,595
(DISTORTED) At last.
终于

736
00:50:53,440 --> 00:50:55,954
I created this tiny object
我创造了这个小东西

737
00:50:57,320 --> 00:51:00,039
and it has bound me in darkness.
而它把我困在了黑暗中

738
00:51:04,600 --> 00:51:06,876
Which of you shall release me?
你们谁来释放我？

739
00:51:13,240 --> 00:51:14,594
(EXPLODING)

740
00:51:15,720 --> 00:51:17,791
Light...
光...

741
00:51:18,720 --> 00:51:20,074
(GROANING)

742
00:51:20,200 --> 00:51:25,434
Symmetry of colours and shapes.
对称的颜色和形状

743
00:51:27,040 --> 00:51:30,829
No more tomb of darkness.
不再有黑暗的坟墓了

744
00:51:33,760 --> 00:51:38,197
My strength is growing again.
我的力量又开始增长了

745
00:51:40,080 --> 00:51:42,276
I grasp it.
我抓住了

746
00:51:42,400 --> 00:51:48,715
Now let my great plan take its shape.
现在让我的伟大计划成形吧

747
00:51:49,360 --> 00:51:51,351
(ENERGY PULSATING)

748
00:51:58,600 --> 00:52:07,319
(ALL CHANTING) Om mani padme hum.
唵嘛呢叭咪吽

749
00:52:13,520 --> 00:52:15,352
TRAVERS: (NORMAL VOICE)
I had a daughter once.
我曾经又一个女儿

750
00:52:16,000 --> 00:52:18,753
What... What happened to her?
怎么...她后来怎么了？

751
00:52:19,520 --> 00:52:20,794
Father?
父亲？

752
00:52:23,080 --> 00:52:26,277
No, no. Not you. Anne.
不, 不, 不是你. 安娜

753
00:52:27,080 --> 00:52:28,036
(CHUCKLES)

754
00:52:28,600 --> 00:52:30,637
Yeti...Travers...I...
雪怪...Travers...我...

755
00:52:33,040 --> 00:52:35,429
I brought it...
我带回了它...

756
00:52:36,640 --> 00:52:38,313
...back from Tibet.
...从西藏带回来

757
00:52:40,880 --> 00:52:42,598
It's all my fault.
这都是我的错

758
00:52:45,280 --> 00:52:47,191
My father died in a cold world,
我的父亲死在了一个冰冷的世界
<i>（她父亲死在 Daleks 母星 Skaro）</i>

759
00:52:48,600 --> 00:52:50,796
a thousand light years away.
一千光年以外

760
00:52:51,560 --> 00:52:54,518
I died 15 years ago.
我15年前就死了

761
00:52:56,280 --> 00:52:57,934
Saw it in The Times.
我在《时代》杂志上看到了

762
00:52:58,520 --> 00:53:00,955
"Professor Edward Travers,”
“爱德华-特拉弗斯教授”

763
00:53:01,520 --> 00:53:02,840
CBE.
大英帝国司令勋章

764
00:53:03,640 --> 00:53:05,313
Silly old fool.
老糊涂

765
00:53:07,000 --> 00:53:07,956
(CHUCKLING)

766
00:53:08,800 --> 00:53:10,916
"No flowers, by request.”
“应家属请求, 不要送花”

767
00:53:12,760 --> 00:53:14,592
But they still sent them.
但他们还是送来了花

768
00:53:16,000 --> 00:53:17,399
No one listens.
没人肯听

769
00:53:18,600 --> 00:53:21,114
Sometimes I can't remember his face.
有时我记不起他的面容

770
00:53:24,960 --> 00:53:26,792
And I've travelled in time.
但我穿越了时间

771
00:53:28,680 --> 00:53:30,478
Where do I belong now?
我现在属于什么地方？

772
00:53:33,920 --> 00:53:35,194
Don't you see?
你不明白吗？

773
00:53:36,640 --> 00:53:37,960
We've been tricked.
我们被耍了

774
00:53:39,120 --> 00:53:42,397
It was the Intelligence all the time!
一直都是大智慧

775
00:53:44,960 --> 00:53:46,792
Unfinished business.
这事没完(?)

776
00:53:46,920 --> 00:53:48,718
(BOOMING)

777
00:53:49,440 --> 00:53:51,477
(LIGHTNING CRASHING)

778
00:54:09,200 --> 00:54:12,200
<i>(Terminal Accessed)</i>
<i>（电脑文字：终端访问已接入）</i>

779
00:54:15,480 --> 00:54:18,313
What now, sir? Take the place by storm?
现在怎样, 长官？顶着暴风雨拿下这个地方？(?)

780
00:54:18,440 --> 00:54:19,794
If we must.
如果必须的话

781
00:54:22,480 --> 00:54:24,790
Damnation. I'm an old fool.
见鬼, 我真是老糊涂了

782
00:54:24,920 --> 00:54:25,955
- Sir?  - My gun.
- 怎么  - 我的枪

783
00:54:26,080 --> 00:54:27,309
I didn't pick it up.
我没拿起来

784
00:54:27,440 --> 00:54:30,512
- Want to go back?
- Too late for that, now. Come on.
- 想回去吗？  - 来不及了. 现在走吧

785
00:54:32,440 --> 00:54:34,351
(DISTORTED) Intruders.
有人入侵

786
00:54:35,480 --> 00:54:39,235
Go. Greet them.
去, 问候一下他们

787
00:54:39,360 --> 00:54:41,431
(ENERGY PULSATING)

788
00:54:49,720 --> 00:54:54,032
Sir, something rotten in here, sir. 
I can feel it.
长官, 这里有什么东西坏掉了, 我能感觉到

789
00:54:54,160 --> 00:54:56,276
Too quiet. Come on.
太安静. 快来

790
00:54:58,160 --> 00:54:59,559
Let's start at the top.
我们先从上面开始

791
00:55:07,720 --> 00:55:09,154
Sorry, sir.
抱歉, 长官

792
00:55:09,280 --> 00:55:12,591
1 give up, Hinton.
Am I asleep or are you dead?
我放弃了, 辛顿. 是我在睡觉还是你死了？

793
00:55:12,720 --> 00:55:14,074
I never did philosophy, sir.
我不玩哲学, 长官

794
00:55:14,200 --> 00:55:16,271
You're in the lift.
I'm in the computer systems.
你在电梯里, 我在电脑系统里

795
00:55:16,400 --> 00:55:17,834
We have interface.
我们就有了交互界面

796
00:55:17,960 --> 00:55:20,679
So I'm talking to a ghost in a machine.
这么说我是在跟机器里面的一个鬼魂说话

797
00:55:21,480 --> 00:55:23,118
And what's the warning this time?
这次又是什么警告？

798
00:55:23,240 --> 00:55:26,358
The Intelligence has got into the
logic systems of New World's computers.
大智慧已经进入新世界的电脑系统了

799
00:55:26,480 --> 00:55:28,039
I snuck a ride too.
我也偷偷搭便车

800
00:55:28,160 --> 00:55:31,357
It's a virus. It's already spreading
across the Internet.
是一种病毒, 已经散布到整个因特网了

801
00:55:31,480 --> 00:55:33,437
Transmitted from this building.
是从这栋建筑传送出去的

802
00:55:33,560 --> 00:55:36,871
I'll take you in as far as I can, sir.
Trust me.
我尽力带你进去, 相信我

803
00:55:37,360 --> 00:55:38,680
You've said that before.
你以前也说过这话

804
00:55:38,800 --> 00:55:39,949
Sir?
长官？

805
00:55:42,080 --> 00:55:44,959
Nothing, Sergeant.
I just walked over someone's grave.
没什么, 上士. 我刚碰到鬼了

806
00:55:46,320 --> 00:55:48,516
Come on, Hinton! Come on!
快啊, 辛顿！快点

807
00:55:58,040 --> 00:55:59,933
- I thought that you were dead.
- Maybe.
- 我以为你已经死了  - 也许

808
00:56:00,400 --> 00:56:02,437
I need your help, Kate. So does your dad.
我需要你的帮助, 凯特, 你爸爸也需要

809
00:56:02,560 --> 00:56:03,516
Right.
好

810
00:56:07,200 --> 00:56:10,158
It's no good, sir. Something's jamming it.
这没用的, 被什么东西卡住了

811
00:56:12,200 --> 00:56:13,429
I'm not used to this system.
我不熟悉这个系统

812
00:56:13,560 --> 00:56:14,630
But I am.
但我熟

813
00:56:14,760 --> 00:56:17,593
Ever heard of automatic writing?
Fingers on the keys.
听说过自动写文章吗？把手指放上去

814
00:56:34,160 --> 00:56:36,834
(HOUSE MUSIC PLAYING
THROUGH HEADPHONES)

815
00:56:44,960 --> 00:56:46,917
HINTON: Something's moving that lift.
有什么东西在控制那个电梯

816
00:56:47,680 --> 00:56:50,672
Option. A-D-stroke-Alt-three. Hit four.
Option键, A-D, 敲Alt-3, 按4

817
00:56:55,440 --> 00:56:56,999
It's like a morgue, sir.
像个停尸房, 长官

818
00:56:58,520 --> 00:56:59,476
Like a trap.
像是个陷阱

819
00:57:00,160 --> 00:57:01,355
Back the other way.
回去那边

820
00:57:14,800 --> 00:57:15,790
HINTON: Stop that lift!
停掉那个电梯

821
00:57:15,920 --> 00:57:17,991
Option, three-stroke-Alt-four.
Option键, Alt-4敲三遍

822
00:57:20,440 --> 00:57:22,158
Brigadier, Get back!
准将, 回去！

823
00:57:22,920 --> 00:57:24,035
You...
你...

824
00:57:24,880 --> 00:57:27,235
Get out of my head.
滚出我的脑袋

825
00:57:27,360 --> 00:57:28,998
I've had enough of your tricks.
我已经受够了你的伎俩

826
00:57:29,520 --> 00:57:32,034
I was wrong. Please!
我之前错了, 求你了！

827
00:57:32,160 --> 00:57:34,310
Get away from the lift!
离开那个电梯！

828
00:57:34,440 --> 00:57:35,839
It's fighting back.
它在反击了

829
00:57:35,960 --> 00:57:37,553
Alt-four again. Hold it down!
再按 Alt-4. 按住了

830
00:57:38,160 --> 00:57:41,835
Come away, please, Brigadier.
You shouldn't have come here.
你走吧, 准将. 你不该来这里的

831
00:57:41,960 --> 00:57:43,917
It's a bit late for apologies, Madam.
现在道歉晚了点吧, 女士

832
00:57:45,600 --> 00:57:46,556
Hold it there!
按住了！

833
00:57:46,680 --> 00:57:48,159
I can't keep it down.
我没法按下去

834
00:57:49,000 --> 00:57:50,752
Go back to your studies.
回去继续学习

835
00:57:50,880 --> 00:57:52,200
There's nothing here you want!
这里没有你们想要的东西

836
00:57:52,320 --> 00:57:53,276
(THUDDING)

837
00:57:53,880 --> 00:57:54,870
Quickly.
快

838
00:58:00,480 --> 00:58:01,675
This way.
这边

839
00:58:02,360 --> 00:58:03,919
HARRODS: Look out, sir!
小心, 长官！

840
00:58:04,840 --> 00:58:06,558
Leave him alone!
放开他！

841
00:58:12,160 --> 00:58:13,559
Hold it down!
按住！

842
00:58:13,680 --> 00:58:14,636
(BANG)

843
00:58:16,440 --> 00:58:18,590
(ROARING)

844
00:58:20,200 --> 00:58:23,397
TRAVERS: Acolytes! You know me!
助手们, 你们认识我的！

845
00:58:24,520 --> 00:58:26,272
Stand away!
都闪开！

846
00:58:26,400 --> 00:58:27,470
Travers?
特拉弗斯？

847
00:58:31,320 --> 00:58:33,789
Release him! Let him go free!
放开他！让他走！

848
00:58:36,600 --> 00:58:38,671
(ROARING)

849
00:58:44,360 --> 00:58:46,397
(SCREAMING)

850
00:58:49,520 --> 00:58:51,158
Must shut down the database.
必须关闭数据库了

851
00:58:52,000 --> 00:58:53,638
VICTORIA: Leave him alone!
放开他！

852
00:58:55,120 --> 00:58:56,918
(ROARING)

853
00:58:57,920 --> 00:59:01,151
All right. I was coming anyway.
好吧. 反正我也会来的

854
00:59:02,240 --> 00:59:05,039
DISTORTED VOICE: What happened
to your faith, old man?
你的信念怎么了, 老头？

855
00:59:05,920 --> 00:59:08,912
Huh? I saw your Light of Truth,
that's what!
哈？我见过你的真理之光了, 这就是怎么了

856
00:59:09,040 --> 00:59:11,156
And I'll put a stop to it!
我必须叫停它！

857
00:59:11,280 --> 00:59:14,398
-(GASPS)
- More intruders, as anticipated.
又有入侵者, 比预期要多

858
00:59:15,560 --> 00:59:17,358
(ALL ROARING)

859
00:59:17,800 --> 00:59:20,314
Travers... (LAUGHING)
特拉弗斯...

860
00:59:20,440 --> 00:59:23,000
You're still my closest instrument!
你仍然是我最好的工具！

861
00:59:31,520 --> 00:59:33,511
(ALL ROARING)

862
00:59:37,400 --> 00:59:39,516
(GUNFIRE)

863
00:59:42,760 --> 00:59:44,433
(GUNFIRE CONTINUES)

864
00:59:48,680 --> 00:59:50,512
This place is like a beacon.
这地方跟一个灯塔似的

865
00:59:50,960 --> 00:59:52,837
It's Kate Lethbridge-Stewart, isn't it?
你是凯特•利斯布里奇-斯图尔特, 对吗？

866
00:59:53,000 --> 00:59:55,037
- But...
- Sarah-Jane Smith. Hello.
- 但是...  - 我是莎拉-简·史密斯, 你好

867
00:59:55,160 --> 00:59:56,958
Your father said it
might be a family affair.
你父亲说这可能是一个家庭事务

868
00:59:57,480 --> 01:00:00,313
- So, show me where to find him.
- All right.
- 所以, 告诉我哪里可以找到他  - 好吧

869
01:00:00,440 --> 01:00:02,477
- EXPLOSIONS)
{GUNFIRE)

870
01:00:05,400 --> 01:00:06,993
(ROARING)

871
01:00:18,200 --> 01:00:19,520
(GRUNTS)

872
01:00:28,560 --> 01:00:30,597
(LIGHTNING CRASHING)

873
01:00:34,280 --> 01:00:35,429
Distract them, Brigadier.
引开他们, 准将

874
01:00:35,560 --> 01:00:38,439
This is my fault. If I can shut down
the mainframe...
这是我的错, 如果我能关闭电脑主机...

875
01:00:38,560 --> 01:00:40,278
I'm sure we've met before.
我敢肯定我们之前见过

876
01:00:40,400 --> 01:00:41,390
I doubt it.
我怀疑没有

877
01:00:42,560 --> 01:00:44,631
(PULSATING)

878
01:00:58,720 --> 01:01:00,757
{ROARING)
{GRUNTS)

879
01:01:12,200 --> 01:01:14,396
(DISTORTED) Bring my jailer here.
带我的狱卒过来

880
01:01:21,120 --> 01:01:24,078
Stop her! This time, destroy her.
阻止她！这次, 消灭她

881
01:01:24,840 --> 01:01:26,990
My strength is growing, jailer.
我的力量在增长, 狱卒

882
01:01:30,120 --> 01:01:32,919
Your defences are powerless to stop me.
你的防御太弱, 阻止不了我

883
01:01:33,040 --> 01:01:35,680
I'm amazed at your awesome ingenuity,
我很惊讶于你的精巧布局

884
01:01:36,680 --> 01:01:37,636
Travers.
特拉弗斯

885
01:01:37,760 --> 01:01:40,036
The late Professor Travers.
已故的特拉弗斯教授

886
01:01:40,720 --> 01:01:42,438
This is my world now.
现在这是我的世界了

887
01:01:42,560 --> 01:01:43,516
Oh, of course.
噢, 当然

888
01:01:44,040 --> 01:01:47,431
I'm doubtless you'll make a better job
of it than we humans have.
毫无疑问你会比我们人类干得好

889
01:01:48,520 --> 01:01:50,750
Sarah, take this. It's for my father.
莎拉, 拿着这个, 这是我父亲的

890
01:01:51,280 --> 01:01:52,634
I'm a rotten shot. You hang onto it.
我枪法很烂, 你留着吧

891
01:01:52,760 --> 01:01:55,479
Look, I don't want to fight.
I want my dad back.
看, 我并不想参战, 我只要我的爸爸回来

892
01:01:56,720 --> 01:01:58,757
Where's the back-up gone to?
后援都去哪儿了？

893
01:02:09,520 --> 01:02:11,477
(ALL ROARING)

894
01:02:19,600 --> 01:02:22,831
We humans are basically
a gregarious species,
我们人类基本上是群居物种

895
01:02:23,680 --> 01:02:24,670
er, Great One,
呃, 大智慧

896
01:02:25,320 --> 01:02:28,153
despite exceptions, like Daniel Hinton.
尽管有些例外, 比如丹尼尔·辛顿

897
01:02:28,280 --> 01:02:30,510
Deleted from my system.
从我的系统里删掉了

898
01:02:30,640 --> 01:02:32,119
Oh, I see.
噢, 我明白了

899
01:02:32,240 --> 01:02:35,153
So, resistance is obviously...
What's the word?
所以, 抵抗显然是...那个词是什么来着？

900
01:02:35,800 --> 01:02:38,394
Useless? Good.
徒劳的？很好

901
01:02:39,440 --> 01:02:41,113
But tell me, Brigadier.
但是告诉我, 准将

902
01:02:42,080 --> 01:02:48,349
Which part of my Great Plan do you think
is most strategically successful?
我的伟大计划中哪一部分你觉得在战略上是最成功的

903
01:02:48,920 --> 01:02:50,752
- None of it.
- What?
- 全都不是  - 什么？

904
01:02:50,880 --> 01:02:53,918
For a so-called Intelligence,
you're pretty damn stupid.
虽然叫做“大智慧”, 其实你相当蠢

905
01:02:54,520 --> 01:02:55,874
You're still trapped.
你还是被困住了

906
01:02:56,000 --> 01:02:58,389
- No.
- That's not a body.
- 不  - 那不是一架躯体

907
01:02:58,520 --> 01:03:02,275
You've trapped yourself
in a web of silicon and cables.
你把自己困在了硅晶和线缆的网里

908
01:03:02,920 --> 01:03:05,992
All of it stolen.
And you can't venture beyond it.
全都是偷来的, 你还不敢冒险超越它

909
01:03:06,560 --> 01:03:09,393
I have slammed the door on my darkness.
我已经关上了黑暗的门

910
01:03:09,520 --> 01:03:14,515
And I shall perpetuate myself in every machine
and every being in my world.
我将长存于我世界中每一台机器, 每一个生命里面

911
01:03:15,280 --> 01:03:16,395
Balderdash.
胡言乱语

912
01:03:18,240 --> 01:03:22,473
Your power goes no further than
the mainframe of this campus.
你的能力跑不出这个园区里面的主机

913
01:03:23,400 --> 01:03:27,792
All anyone has to do is to pull the plug.
任何人只要拔下插头就可以了

914
01:03:28,560 --> 01:03:29,516
(MOUTHING)

915
01:03:30,600 --> 01:03:31,829
Stay out of sight till I'm back.
躲起来直到我回来为止

916
01:03:31,960 --> 01:03:33,030
No, Sarah.
不, 莎拉

917
01:03:33,160 --> 01:03:35,151
Protect the generators.
保护发电机

918
01:03:38,480 --> 01:03:43,873
I shall burrow deep into the Earth's roots
and reach high into its skies.
我将下潜入地底, 上飞于天空

919
01:03:45,000 --> 01:03:49,153
And the humans shall provide me
with new machines
而且人类会为我提供新的机器

920
01:03:49,760 --> 01:03:52,115
and new bodies.
和新的身体

921
01:03:56,760 --> 01:03:57,716
Dad!
爸爸！

922
01:03:59,040 --> 01:03:59,996
Kate.
凯特

923
01:04:00,680 --> 01:04:04,389
COMPUTER: (REPEATING) Access denied.
拒绝访问

924
01:04:04,520 --> 01:04:05,476
(WHIZZING)

925
01:04:07,080 --> 01:04:10,710
Access denied, Victoria, my dear.
访问被拒了, 维多利亚, 我亲爱的

926
01:04:10,840 --> 01:04:12,194
It's not too late.
还不算太迟

927
01:04:12,320 --> 01:04:14,038
Way, way out of time.
太, 太迟了

928
01:04:14,920 --> 01:04:17,355
Let's see what the New World has in store.
让我们看看新世界里面都存有些什么

929
01:04:17,480 --> 01:04:19,391
- Get away from her!
-(GUNSHOT)
离她远点！

930
01:04:21,400 --> 01:04:22,629
Turn off the power!
关闭电源！

931
01:04:22,760 --> 01:04:23,909
That's what I'm trying to do!
我正要干这个！

932
01:04:24,040 --> 01:04:24,996
(GUNSHOT)

933
01:04:26,240 --> 01:04:27,196
I'm sorry, Dad.
对不起, 爸爸

934
01:04:28,360 --> 01:04:29,350
As bad as your mother.
跟你母亲一样差

935
01:04:29,480 --> 01:04:31,790
Oh, you have blood ties.
噢, 你们有血缘纽带

936
01:04:31,920 --> 01:04:34,639
Very well. I need more Yetis.
很好, 我还需要些雪怪

937
01:04:34,840 --> 01:04:36,114
She can be the next.
她可以是下一个

938
01:04:42,840 --> 01:04:44,592
(ROARING)
(GUNSHOT)

939
01:04:44,760 --> 01:04:45,955
Ah!
啊！

940
01:04:47,120 --> 01:04:48,076
Daniel?
丹尼尔？

941
01:04:48,200 --> 01:04:49,873
(GROWLING)

942
01:04:50,680 --> 01:04:51,750
Daniel.
丹尼尔

943
01:04:52,560 --> 01:04:54,437
I know you're still clinging there.
我知道你还在那里

944
01:04:54,560 --> 01:04:55,516
(ROARING)

945
01:04:55,680 --> 01:04:58,672
Daniel, remember your disciplines.
丹尼尔, 记住你的纪律

946
01:04:59,520 --> 01:05:01,909
Daniel, fight the evil.
丹尼尔, 同邪恶斗争

947
01:05:02,320 --> 01:05:04,118
Remember your inner strength.
记住你的内在力量

948
01:05:05,520 --> 01:05:09,514
Remember the sword that cuts through
the thorns of deceit.
记住那把剑, 斩断欺骗的荆棘

949
01:05:10,400 --> 01:05:11,879
Be that sword, Daniel!
成为那把剑吧, 丹尼尔

950
01:05:12,680 --> 01:05:13,750
Remember!
记住！

951
01:05:13,880 --> 01:05:15,951
-(ROARING)
-(LAUGHING)

952
01:05:16,880 --> 01:05:18,279
(SPHERE BEEPING)

953
01:05:23,920 --> 01:05:25,957
(GUNSHOTS)

954
01:05:34,760 --> 01:05:36,671
- Daniel?
-(LAUGHING)
丹尼尔？

955
01:05:36,800 --> 01:05:38,074
You're dead.
你死了

956
01:05:38,880 --> 01:05:40,917
(SCREAMING)

957
01:05:41,760 --> 01:05:45,276
No, Daniel! Destroy the generators!
不, 丹尼尔！摧毁发电机！

958
01:05:53,360 --> 01:05:54,794
I am not defeated!
我没被打败！

959
01:05:54,920 --> 01:05:56,479
Leave our world alone!
离开我们的世界！

960
01:05:57,160 --> 01:05:58,514
It's my world!
这是我的世界！

961
01:05:58,640 --> 01:06:01,029
Go back to Hell, you're not wanted here.
回到地狱去吧, 这里不欢迎你

962
01:06:02,160 --> 01:06:04,231
(GROANING AND WHIMPERING)

963
01:06:10,040 --> 01:06:12,077
(ENERGY PULSATING)

964
01:06:20,760 --> 01:06:22,751
(PULSATING)

965
01:06:37,440 --> 01:06:38,555
Dad.
爸爸

966
01:06:38,680 --> 01:06:40,114
It's all right, Kate. It's gone.
没事了, 凯特, 它消失了

967
01:06:40,840 --> 01:06:42,751
This time, it's gone for good.
这一次, 它永远离开了

968
01:06:42,880 --> 01:06:45,838
Brigadier! Brigadier!
准将！准将！

969
01:06:45,960 --> 01:06:49,669
Miss Smith. I knew there was someone here
I could rely on.
史密斯小姐, 我就知道至少还有一个人我可以信赖

970
01:06:50,320 --> 01:06:52,231
- Oh, have you two, er...
- Yes. We've met.
- 噢, 你们俩是不是...  - 是的, 我们见过

971
01:06:52,880 --> 01:06:54,757
It's just like old times, eh?
就跟以前一样, 嗯？

972
01:06:54,880 --> 01:06:57,554
And I still don't know what's going on.
(LAUGHING)
我还是不知道发生了什么

973
01:06:57,680 --> 01:07:00,718
Well, someone else can clear up. Let's just go home.
嗯, 会有人来收拾的. 我们还是回家吧

974
01:07:21,140 --> 01:07:24,098
So, he said it was Victoria's dress.
于是, 他说这是维多利亚的裙子
<i>（见第十三季第三集《火星的金字塔》）</i>

975
01:07:25,140 --> 01:07:28,212
And I said, "Well, as long as
Albert didn't wear it."”
然后我说：“哦, 只要阿尔伯特没有穿过”

976
01:07:29,260 --> 01:07:31,171
And you think it could have been her.
所以你认为这可能是她

977
01:07:31,300 --> 01:07:34,816
1 don't know. There's no trace of her.
She just vanished into thin air.
我不知道,  没有她的踪迹, 她就那样凭空消失了

978
01:07:36,020 --> 01:07:38,330
Certain people we know make a habit of that.
我们认识的某些人是有这样的习惯

979
01:07:39,140 --> 01:07:40,414
(BOTH CHUCKLING)

980
01:07:42,500 --> 01:07:46,778
Do you know, companions used to be
something only dowager aunts had.
你知道吗, 同伴以前是只有老年贵妇人才有的

981
01:07:46,900 --> 01:07:50,177
No, Sarah, it applies to families as well.
不, 莎拉, 这对家庭也适用

982
01:07:51,100 --> 01:07:53,011
Oh, yes, families.
噢, 是的, 家庭

983
01:07:57,540 --> 01:08:01,454
Dad, this is Gordon.
Gordy, say hello to granddad.
爸爸, 这是戈登. 戈迪, 跟外公说你好

984
01:08:01,580 --> 01:08:02,729
Hello, Gordy.
你好, 戈迪

985
01:08:04,100 --> 01:08:05,374
You're not shy, are you?
你不害羞, 是吧？

986
01:08:06,980 --> 01:08:09,096
I've got another friend too.
我也另外有个朋友

987
01:08:09,540 --> 01:08:11,053
Oh? What's his name?
噢, 他叫什么名字？

988
01:08:11,180 --> 01:08:13,569
Danny. But only I can see him.
丹尼, 但只有我能看见他

989
01:08:14,380 --> 01:08:15,336
Oh.
噢

990
01:08:21,260 --> 01:08:22,216
Oh.
哦

991
01:08:24,940 --> 01:08:27,436
Well, you'd better tell me all about him.
那, 你最好把他的事都告诉我

992
01:08:31,380 --> 01:08:33,849
I'm ravenous. Fancy a pizza?
我饿死了, 对披萨有兴趣吗？

993
01:08:33,980 --> 01:08:36,130
You know, I think I'd rather have a pint.
知道不, 我想我更愿意一杯

994
01:08:36,260 --> 01:08:38,092
Make it a cup of tea, and you're on.
泡上一杯茶, 你就高兴起来了 (?)


995
01:08:38,220 --> 01:08:39,494
(BOTH LAUGHING)

996
